CWINDOW library 0.3 (c) by Stefan Schimanski & Janko Heilgeist  - 1Stein@gmx.de
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following makefiles are included:

makefile.bc  - Borland C++ 3.1
makefile.gcc - DJGPP 2.x
makefile.wat - Watcom C/C++ 10.x

The libraries are created in the subdirectory LIBS.
The directory DEMO includes a demo that demonstrates the library.

